The paper discusses a machine learning technique (knowledge tracing) and proposes a novel regularization method to improve its reliability. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and education (cs.EDU). Among these, machine learning and artificial intelligence are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the topic of the paper. Natural language processing and cybersecurity are also relevant as they are mentioned in the paper as perspectives from which the limitations of DLKT are discussed. Education is also a likely category as the paper discusses the application of knowledge tracing in education environments.
